data.description: Situated on over half an acre w/peekaboo views of Big Lake & the Cascade foothills. Welcome to Nookachamp Hills w/this updated 4bd, 2.5ba, 3,300 sqft home. This elegant home offers a primary suite featuring a lg walk-in closet & spa-like bath. Vaulted ceilings, & seamless integrated living & dining areas. Kitchen w/natural light, granite counters, stainless appliances. Bonus office & finished basement suite. Private partially fenced yard, porch, & deck are perfect for entertaining. RV parking (50-amp hookup). Forced air heating/cooling. Don't miss out on this stunning property with private access to Otter pond, where you can swim, practice catch and release fishing, or enjoy the trails. Country setting just minutes to town.
